longBusinessSummary: A B Infrabuild Limited provides construction and related allied services in India. The company is involved in designing, engineering, procurement, and construction of railway platforms, station buildings, gauge conversion, and laying of railway tracks; and construction of beam, cantilever, arch, suspension, cable-stayed, and truss bridges, as well as bituminous and concrete roads. It also undertakes dam works, such as gravity, arch, saddle, and check dams; piling dirt, earthworks, piles friction setting, and other activities to build canals or reservoirs; and repair and petty road works, and renovation and reconstruction works of slum areas. A B Infrabuild Limited was founded in 1999 and is based in Mumbai, India.
